== Purpose of the Statement of Cash Flows

1. Predicts future cashflows
2. Evaluates management decisions
3. Determines ability to pay dividends and interest
4. Use to assess the relationship of net income to cash Flows
5. Use to cmpare operating performance

== Cash FLow Categories

1. Operating Activity - Net income, current asset, current liability
2. Investing Activity - Long-term asset
3. Financing Activity - Long-term liabilities and owner's equity


